journalist_caption: Palestinians gather to perform Eid al-Adha prayer among the rubble of buildings destroyed by Israeli forces.

Children collect food donated by a charity. The Israeli army said this week it would observe a limited daily tactical pause along one of the main roads in the Gaza Strip to allow the delivery of increased quantities of humanitarian aid as UN agencies suspended deliveries from a US-built pier.
Merih Demiral displayed the wolf salute after scoring in Turkeys round of 16 match against Austria.
